title: Dumpling
description:
A dumpling of dough and filling, as folded and pinched closed for steaming or frying. Associated with cuisines around the world, including China (jiaozi), Japan (gyoza or dango), Poland (pierogi), and Spain and Latin America (empanada).

Facebook's design previously resembled a xiaolongbao, a Chinese soup dumpling.
apple_vendor_description: This delightful dumpling emoji on Apple devices is depicted with a plump, slightly translucent wrapper, hinting at a savory filling within. Apple's characteristic glossy 3D shading and realistic lighting make it look incredibly appetizing, with subtle folds and a warm, inviting sheen. It's a charming way to represent comfort food, a delicious meal, or a craving for something satisfying in your messages.
